{"tid":1207181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生增援黎緊","createTime":"2019-06-12T05:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T06:00:14.000Z","uid":219211,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e68d23ba4fe33a2b8ea03998d405e639b1c74688","tid":1207181,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"各位頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d970c6795866a61da20e3d247f4fabb6656c2109","tid":1207181,"uid":4739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:27:30.000Z","msg":"有人用棍拍野deam beat 既時候唔好劣<br />\n一齊叫同一句口號加士氣避免士氣此消彼長<br />\n有心理學背後原理<br />\n對陣口號可參考港隊打氣口號<br />\n拍拍~拍拍拍~DIE FOR HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n引用 雞肉大師 巴打:<br />\n要佢哋一齊嘶哮， 進入同一個呼吸節奏 同一個心跳步伐 <br />\n配合戰鼓(你搵個大水樽好撚大嗰啲 求其搵嘢敲佢有節奏嘅)打拍子 就會將一堆散兵游勇聚合成一個群體<br />\n以往慣例邊個大聲公喇叭就死邊個， 二來呢啲設備貴<br />\n但係水樽就可以有好多個 水樽買得起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家小心雙眼，戴眼罩被人噴油漆就喪失視力，唔戴又會比人插眼<br />\n<br />\n大家亦小心近距離突然由下巴向上大力推有機會導致頸椎受傷 請各位注意安全免生危險<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVyedqs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVyedqs.png&h=8e0592eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53b386fa326358744b1babb67e99bffdd76cfc29","tid":1207181,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"好多人黎緊"},{"pid":"b914c9fe223a145956433add062bddf84cd15863","tid":1207181,"uid":205252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"求下大家堅持住 小弟不行了 要返去休一休息 陣間再戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73195cf6c83f5527bcd18cd348e10515062ba73","tid":1207181,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b914c9fe223a145956433add062bddf84cd15863","tid":1207181,"uid":205252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"求下大家堅持住 小弟不行了 要返去休一休息 陣間再戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:33:18.000Z","msg":"保重！"},{"pid":"2f538eaf3be13391f2cca697681f586486d9f5ad","tid":1207181,"uid":50835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGVXa0P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGVXa0P.png&h=1f7c1112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重要：要求政府今日下午3點前撤回方案, 否則：<br />\n<br />\n- 不排除衝入立法會行動<br />\n- 無限期罷課罷工罷巿<br />\n- 無限期阻塞中環至灣仔交通<br />\n- 無限期暫停繳交所有政府稅收、費用、罰款<br />\n- 癱瘓鐵路系統<br />\n- 包圍主要官員官邸<br />\n大家請廣傳, 唔可以再比人拖唔係會同5年前一樣, SET deadline and target比義士等佢地唔洗無了期打消耗戰!!"},{"pid":"e93f5f6ec678eea6a5b3631077de7f5ddedaddf2","tid":1207181,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"各位同學一定要有口罩,萬事小心"},{"pid":"bcdfb0977c551424f006bc65f4bf70c1090d63d7","tid":1207181,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">地鐵 太多人</spa